{"tid":1375224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有關遊行叫嘅口號","createTime":"2019-07-28T04:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T05:24:44.000Z","uid":273272,"like":18,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"267deafd4fe3b71352c6b1e153c786bd3c0718ee","tid":1375224,"uid":273272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:09:24.000Z","msg":"除咗<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「光復香港，時代革命」</span></strong></span>之外，唔該大家叫啲有氣勢啲嘅口號，特別係和理非。<br />\n<br />\n唔該大家咪叫「香港警察，知法犯法」啦，叫到就算有幾大聲，又有乜意思呢，班垃圾法都唔撚知，同埋好尻多公安法都係好有問題，知法又代表乜。班畜牲聽到笑尻你哋傻仔喳。<br />\n<br />\n試吓叫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「香港警察，吞槍自殺」</strong></span></span>（係借用之前一位巴打嘅提議）。你想像吓佢哋會有乜反應？<br />\n<br />\n咪再叫，「黑警，可恥」，佢哋知羞恥嘅咩？要叫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「黑警，冚家鏟！」</span></strong></span>佢哋嘅所作所為，咪同我講禍不及家人，係禍必及家人！<br />\n<br />\n咪再叫，乜鬼「林鄭，落台」，落乜台呀，佢落台件事就完㗎啦，依個幾月嘅鬥爭都會付諸流水，要叫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「林鄭，落地獄！」</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔勇武都好，唔該顯示出大家嘅怒火啦，咪話會激起班畜牲嘅情緒，令佢哋更加暴力，佢哋而家點都係癲狗咁。反而我哋要俾佢哋知道，全香港嘅市民，都係極度厭惡你班警渣，恨不得要你哋死清光，要令佢哋草木皆兵，壓力爆煲。我哋做得幾多使幾多。"},{"pid":"030ddfbadfefa447c283008143fa298a35c9e691","tid":1375224,"uid":273272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:09:44.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9961c1d78b05c4df88c8699554b3e69cc9512f08","tid":1375224,"uid":55917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81fb92d7fedbca92be52dc2fd31cfc5112b5672","tid":1375224,"uid":273272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:09:54.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6926295e8f95c56609cf64ba71c6671e6a47610","tid":1375224,"uid":214192,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:10:48.000Z","msg":"林鄭下台真係唔好再叫<br />\n講左十萬次，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭係落地獄</span></span>"},{"pid":"1bd5e07b39d390034bb6c8bd78c0aeff21d22459","tid":1375224,"uid":273272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:10:55.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf8563ab7ce76ded68de0c11358e353afbb2dcf","tid":1375224,"uid":273272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:11:08.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f431cf1865b6b098cae92ac0b39e463a5e3a253","tid":1375224,"uid":273272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:11:53.000Z","msg":"幫手推吓，如果叫得口號，叫啲有意思嘅"},{"pid":"b11634ade163229b611dc3de183df2fb040bb7d5","tid":1375224,"uid":273272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:12:03.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d87b86742c0299e5d943cbc412aa3b003c19cc","tid":1375224,"uid":273272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:12:13.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/